@node BOUNT "Bounty of the Hunt"

@{b}Bounty of the Hunt@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = AI(U2)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 3GG
Artist  = Jeff A. Menges

Text(AI): You may remove a green card in your hand from the game instead
          of paying Bounty of the Hunt's casting cost. Put three +1/+1
          counters, distributed any way you choose, on any number of
          target creatures. Remove these counters at end of turn.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BOUNT}

