@{b}Nature's Wrath@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = AI(R2)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 4GG
Artist  = Liz Danforth

Text(AI): During your upkeep, pay <G> or bury Nature's Wrath. Whenever
